00:07:29.420 --> 00:07:31.140
What Rutherford did
at the Cavendish Lab

00:07:31.140 --> 00:07:34.800
in the 1910s and 1920s
come up with what

00:07:34.800 --> 00:07:36.540
is a mid-level abstraction.

00:07:36.540 --> 00:07:39.117
He had one guiding principle,
