00:07:43.100 --> 00:07:45.530
We're going to find out
what's inside the atom.

00:07:45.530 --> 00:07:47.710
Nothing more, nothing less.

00:07:47.710 --> 00:07:49.240
It's a perfect idea.

00:07:49.240 --> 00:07:51.290
With that, everybody
understands what's going on,

00:07:51.290 --> 00:07:53.790
