not telling them what to do.

00:07:53.790 --> 00:07:55.290
You give them a
real lot of freedom,

00:07:55.290 --> 00:07:56.980
but they're still
pulling together.

00:07:56.980 --> 00:07:59.170
Saint Exupery, the
French poet, once said,

00:07:59.170 --> 00:08:00.920
