into each other's eyes.

00:08:00.920 --> 00:08:02.862
It's looking together
in the same direction.

00:08:02.862 --> 00:08:04.820
If you've ever been in
a poisonous organization

00:08:04.820 --> 00:08:06.780
where people are pulling
in different directions.

00:08:06.780 --> 00:08:08.510
You don't quite understand
what's going on.

00:08:08.510 --> 00:08:09.440
You don't people
don't understand

00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:10.640
why they should
work with each other

00:08:10.640 --> 00:08:12.110
you'll know how
important that was.

00:08:12.110 --> 00:08:14.240
Mid-level abstraction
was wonderful.

00:08:14.240 --> 00:08:14.960
Second question.

00:08:14.960 --> 00:08:17.599
