People tell me it's
beautiful, but please

00:38:00.208 --> 00:38:01.490
don't play it in my presence.

00:38:01.490 --> 00:38:03.590
But as for the aesthetics,
that would be it.

00:38:03.590 --> 00:38:05.680
And when Einstein was
dissatisfied and unhappy,

